Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.34,0:00:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦前往Altair…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.78,0:00:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女性要么就死 要么就变成男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么说Mix也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经不再是我们所认识的Mix了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.59,0:00:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连记忆都丧失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡和柚叶没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体检结果也没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.37,0:00:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是在那里再多待一会儿的话 我们也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.49,0:00:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃还没有回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她出去找不动总司令还没回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特的情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.22,0:00:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说暂时脱离生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.36,0:00:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但需要静养
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总司令不在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特也因用尽了力量而卧病在床
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Neo DEAVA已经不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要轻易放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:00:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们并非到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重整旗鼓 再度进军Altair界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.93,0:01:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要救出Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.10,0:01:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在夺回Mix之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直…一直穷追不舍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:28.58,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:35.78,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,反転する世界のプラトニック 愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:51.43,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,僕らが見てる世界は いつでも逆さまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:02:01.90,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしようもないことで たいがい決まってく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:13.98,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,涙するほど傷つく瞳 心で叫びながら黙っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:24.57,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,最後のふたり 混ざれないまま 秒読みが聞こえてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:30.73,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:36.58,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,すたれゆく動物みたいに愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:40.95,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,泣きたいくらい君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:44.29,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,反転する世界のプラトニック
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:47.30,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,感じたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:28.58,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:35.78,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们在倒错的精神世界中相爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:51.43,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我们眼里的世界总是相互颠倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:02:01.90,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,这几乎要被认定为是无可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:13.98,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口淌泪的眼眸 在内心沉默地叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:24.57,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的两人来不及结合便听到离别的倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:30.73,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:36.58,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们像渐趋衰老的动物一样相爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:40.95,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:44.29,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,在倒错的精神世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:47.30,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我想细细体会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:03:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:02:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只差一点就能看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个世界合奏究极的爱的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在优先养好身体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能在生命之火熄灭之前完成曲子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过你的绝望预知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝望的未来什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有些旋律正因在绝望中演奏才显得优美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曲子完成了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能和我一起演奏吗 挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不动总司令什么时候才会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃那边也没有任何联络
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一个如何 须绪美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 深夜进食高热量的东西有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有慌张的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不动肯定会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连同创圣的神话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草绿色头发的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得帮你打开了次元门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你履行约定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我许下了什么约定?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想不起来也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待时机一成熟 约定自然会得以履行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那时已算是看过她的大胸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛…虽然完全不是大胸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪 你在这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不坐在这里的话我会下沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是…Mix填补的洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙填补过的地方的分子结构完全没有间隙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就算我的力量失控也不会随便下沉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:06:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算把Mix夺回来…我对Mix…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对变成了男人的Mix…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能一如既往地保持爱意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说怎么会没有味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于合为一体了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波隆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这边 阿波隆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们终于能相见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是来接我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭女人 我们不是什么阿波隆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是阿马神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别走 臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也和我合为一体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合掌之间有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左手和右手 天使和人 男人和女人 阴和阳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在其狭缝里到底有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在于左右手狭缝间的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明什么都没有 却好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这好像之前也在哪里听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在天地初开后不久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界充满着美丽的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花草在歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往来不断的昆虫和圣兽在细说情话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使在繁星闪耀的高空中共谐连理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而可怕的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些天使是会狩猎人类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斗争中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称为杀戮天使的阿波罗尼亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邂逅了名叫瑟利雅的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人随即坠入爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波罗尼亚斯背叛了同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站到了人类的一边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后罪人阿波罗尼亚斯舍弃了翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人类一起操纵着巨大的力量--机械天使
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和众天使战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:10:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是创圣之书流所记载的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一万二千年前的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是时间追溯到再上一个轮回…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二万四千年前的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后命运再度轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神话将再次被传承
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神话将再次…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔·空 你想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不记得有下达出击命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不允许你擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉她在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃在向我求救
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我必须快点出发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再目送重要的人的背影…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 到你心爱之人的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后回到太阳之翼的身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一半的你 是时候睁开眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vector Z
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依然切断着通信 所在位置也不明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能用你的绝望预知确定阿马塔的位置吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和御子乃初次邂逅的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创圣之书所述的光与暗狭缝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶舱里面空空如也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和阿马塔初次邂逅的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也是我们初次合体的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那场战斗过后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有听说过这里被认定为严重监视区域
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到居然会变成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃也在这一带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的预知是这么告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然是追着御子乃来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们暂且先分头寻找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:13:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会有这么多…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是我贴的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里到底有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未影为什么让我到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这气味…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前 我来过这座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆的封印 总算被解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“Aquaria舞动于空”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡 你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是追着阿马塔过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉克蕾雅理事长的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟怪炎一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…抱歉 因为我无视了命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座城市 现在被认定为严重监视区域
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说已下达了避难命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:17:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 所以老板他们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不惜违反命令也要到这座城市来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉御子乃在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕要等一万二千年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔之前是在这个电影院里工作的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在这里邂逅了御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个…下一个一万二千年后…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要经人类之手编撰的虚假故事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过不久真正的神话就会在这世上苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 奔跑吧 爱的野兽们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奔往约定之地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 拔不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要管我了 阿马塔你快逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我不能丢下婕希卡不管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔 找你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了 怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山茶花?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vector Y? 莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是约好曲子完成了的话就一起演奏的吗 挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 以那种身体状态合体的话 你的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有时间犹豫了 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍身合体 GO Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 要腐坏了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion SPADA
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了 窝囊废阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳之翼如今正准备觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了很过分的事情 原谅我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…难道那时候看到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我还以为是幻影什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一事无成的窝囊废阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.09,0:22:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.02,0:22:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------ED-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:58.45,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}君へ続く坂道に 白い花が咲いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.59,0:23:06.26,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}夢から覚めたあとも 悲しい空見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:16.24,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}この気持ち葉っぱの裏に住んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.10,0:23:25.74,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}朝露が落ちる音に 耳をすませてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:33.60,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神様 あなたが造った世界は 完璧じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:41.19,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}ここでは毎日恋がポロポロ 死んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:45.38,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}はじめて好きになったの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.53,0:23:48.54,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}あなたは知らないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.67,0:23:53.07,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}地球の裏側でいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.25,0:23:56.28,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.47,0:24:00.61,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}私を忘れてもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:07.12,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:58.45,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}延伸到你身旁的坡道 点缀着雪白色的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.59,0:23:06.26,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}从睡梦中惊醒之后 远望着忧伤的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:16.24,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}这份青涩的感觉 依存在绿叶错综的纹路之间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.10,0:23:25.74,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}侧耳聆听 晨露缓缓落下的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:33.60,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神明您所创造的这个世界并不完美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:41.19,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}因为这里每天都有恋情一段接一段地告终
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:45.38,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我是初尝恋爱的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.53,0:23:48.54,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}这个你应该不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.67,0:23:53.07,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即便永不见天日也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.25,0:23:56.28,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.47,0:24:00.61,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}就算你把我忘却也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:07.12,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身边
